{"tid":2293883,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"CCTVB：國安處已鎖定部份人，未能確定所有參與遊行人是中大學生","createTime":"2020-11-20T14:38:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-20T15:00:41.000Z","uid":219007,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"502828052d6facdfdef08cbe35feaf2cd207b060","tid":2293883,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T14:38:41.000Z","msg":"警方國安處入中大搜證　校園保安帶路　據報已鎖定部分人<br />\n<br />\n警務處國安處今日（20 日）下午派員中大搜集證據，相信是調查校園出現抗爭標語塗鴉，及昨日「畢業遊行」參與者展示抗爭標語和叫喊口號事件。大批警員約下午 3 時許分頭進入校園，並由一名中大保安處職員協助帶路，向警方展示不同照片及文件，先後前往敬文書院、聯合書院、新亞書院等的多幢建築物外，拍照多處懷疑曾被塗鴉的牆壁，搜證的警員在黃昏前陸續離開。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">無綫新聞引述消息報道，據了解警方國安處已鎖定部分人，會向中大索取閉路電視片段調查。消息又指未能確定昨日參與的人全部是中大學生。 </span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E8%99%95%E5%85%A5%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E6%90%9C%E8%AD%89-%E6%A0%A1%E5%9C%92%E4%BF%9D%E5%AE%89%E5%B8%B6%E8%B7%AF-%E6%93%9A%E5%A0%B1%E5%B7%B2%E9%8E%96%E5%AE%9A%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E4%BA%BA/?fbclid=IwAR32ICFq15YvW3pd7pDkvh_hsQW6BHE-wUwUXY2bZfi5MQqcssQSB3GxEzQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E8%2599%2595%25E5%2585%25A5%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2590%259C%25E8%25AD%2589-%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E5%259C%2592%25E4%25BF%259D%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%25B8%25B6%25E8%25B7%25AF-%25E6%2593%259A%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E9%258E%2596%25E5%25AE%259A%25E9%2583%25A8%25E5%2588%2586%25E4%25BA%25BA%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR32ICFq15YvW3pd7pDkvh_hsQW6BHE-wUwUXY2bZfi5MQqcssQSB3GxEzQ&d=gxBKi3yaaNwv0eARaXv6BegAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=31b575ca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E8%2599%2595%25E5%2585%25A5%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2590%259C%25E8%25AD%2589-%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E5%259C%2592%25E4%25BF%259D%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%25B8%25B6%25E8%25B7%25AF-%25E6%2593%259A%2